              Espaço reservado para o carrossel. Vamos implementar depois com
              React island.
            </p>

            <div class="mt-6 h-[220px] w-full rounded-2xl bg-neutral-100"></div>
          </div>

          <div
            class="flex items-center justify-between border-t border-neutral-200 px-6 py-6 text-xs text-neutral-500"
          >
            <span>Carrossel placeholder</span>
            <div class="flex gap-2">
              <span
                class="flex h-8 w-8 items-center justify-center rounded-full border"
                >‹</span
              >
              <span
